<subpara id="RM000001G9L00SX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001G9L00SX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000048S00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT COOLER (SOLAR SENSOR) THERMISTOR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="E225715E02" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Connect the connector.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to ON.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Measure the voltage according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard Voltage</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="3" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.37in"/>
<colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 - 2</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Sensor not exposed to sunlight or inspection light</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 0.8 V</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 - 2</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Sensor exposed to sunlight or inspection light</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>0.8 to 4.3 V</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the resistance is not as specified, replace the cooler (solar sensor) thermistor.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Check from the rear of the connector while it is connected to the cooler (solar sensor) thermistor.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Use an incandescent light for inspection. Bring it within about 30 cm (11.8 in.) of the cooler (solar sensor) thermistor.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
<table>
